    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a mechanically robust example of BMW\u2019s high-revving pinnacle. Powered by the S65 4.0L V8 featuring individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline, the engine delivers linear power and immediate throttle response. The chassis maintains its composure through M-Variable Differential Lock and Electronic Damper Control (EDC), ensuring optimal mechanical grip. Recent service includes critical preventative rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators. The M-DCT dual-clutch transmission remains crisp under load. While showing minor signs of use, the structural integrity of the carbon fiber roof and subframe is excellent, making this a prime candidate for the discerning driver.",
