    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presented in a timeless Obsidian Black Metallic, this 2019 Luxury Touring Sedan has been cared for with an enthusiast's eye. The exterior maintains a high-gloss finish, showing only minor road-pebble marks on the lower front bumper consistent with careful highway use. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of Charcoal leather and brushed aluminum; the upholstery is firm and free of tears, though there is light, natural creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. This is a smoke-free, pet-free vehicle with a panoramic sunroof that operates silently. Mechanically, the car is robust, having followed a strict synthetic oil change regimen every 5,000 miles. All onboard technology, including the premium surround-sound system and adaptive cruise control, is fully operational. The tires were replaced last season and have significant tread remaining. It drives straight, brakes smoothly, and offers a refined experience for its next owner. Includes a full set of weather-resistant floor mats and all original manuals.",
